    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced high-pressure VANOS system. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain features a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is further refined with Bilstein dampers, ensuring sharp turn-in and exceptional lateral stability. While the finish shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the powertrain and structural integrity are dialed for the serious driver.",
