    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in a sophisticated Metallic Silver finish. This vehicle has been a reliable, high-performance daily driver that has always been garaged and treated with care. \n\nExterior: The paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine. Upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, consistent with careful road use. The 19-inch alloy wheels are in great shape, paired with premium all-season tires that offer excellent grip and significant tread life. \n\nInterior: The cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium black leather upholstery. The driver\u2019s seat shows light softening of the side bolster, but the leather remains supple and free of tears. All interior electronics, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the high-fidelity 12-speaker sound system, operate exactly as they should. The dual-zone climate control is powerful and responsive.\n\nMechanical: This car is mechanically robust. It has a comprehensive service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The turbocharged engine delivers smooth, linear power, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. I recently replaced the brake pads and performed a multi-point inspection to ensure everything is in order for the next owner. \n\nThis is a complete package for someone looking for luxury and performance without the 'new car' depreciation. I have the clean title and all service records ready for a smooth transition.",
